"/><figcaption>李渊画像，可见肩膀非常宽</figcaption></figure><p class=\"ztext-empty-paragraph\"><br/></p><figure data-size=\"normal\"><noscript><img src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-e8d9e16f24b9a260fbcfe9199bb5315c_hd.jpg?source=1940ef5c\" data-rawwidth=\"400\" data-rawheight=\"509\" data-size=\"normal\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic4.zhimg.com/50/v2-707979eb772198ca194780bd9b38b187_hd.jpg?source=1940ef5c\" class=\"content_image\" width=\"400\"/></noscript><img src=\"data:image/svg+xml;utf8,&lt;svg xmlns=&#39;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg&#39; width=&#39;400&#39; height=&#39;509&#39;&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;\" data-rawwidth=\"400\" data-rawheight=\"509\" data-size=\"normal\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic4.zhimg.com/50/v2-707979eb772198ca194780bd9b38b187_hd.jpg?source=1940ef5c\" class=\"content_image lazy\" width=\"400\" data-actualsrc=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-e8d9e16f24b9a260fbcfe9199bb5315c_hd.jpg?source=1940ef5c\"/><figcaption>玄宗画像，可见体格不如祖先</figcaption></figure><p class=\"ztext-empty-paragraph\"><br/></p><figure data-size=\"normal\"><noscript><img src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-26006c2e17f599df6665cd773ff6a783_hd.jpg?source=1940ef5c\" data-rawwidth=\"600\" data-rawheight=\"667\" data-size=\"normal\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic4.zhimg.com/50/v2-8c222e30c41799988cb9a9d93f28fb89_hd.jpg?source=1940ef5c\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"600\" data-original=\"https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-26006c2e17f599df6665cd773ff6a783_r.jpg?source=1940ef5c\"/></noscript><img src=\"data:image/svg+xml;utf8,&lt;svg xmlns=&#39;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg&#39; width=&#39;600&#39; height=&#39;667&#39;&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;\" data-rawwidth=\"600\" data-rawheight=\"667\" data-size=\"normal\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic4.zhimg.com/50/v2-8c222e30c41799988cb9a9d93f28fb89_hd.jpg?source=1940ef5c\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"600\" data-original=\"https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-26006c2e17f599df6665cd773ff6a783_r.jpg?source=1940ef5c\" d